'''愛德華·史考特·普魯特'''（{{lang-en|Edward Scott Pruitt}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sbts.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2010/11/Catalog_directory_Aug2013.pdf |title=Southern Seminary Catalog – Directory, 2013–2014 |accessdate=2017-03-05 |archive-date=2016-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220151011/http://www.sbts.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2010/11/Catalog_directory_Aug2013.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>；{{bd|1968年|5月9日|}}），是[[美國|美國]][[奧克拉荷馬州|奧克拉荷馬州]]一名律師和政治人物，第14任[[美国国家环境保护局|美国国家环境保护局]]局長。自1998年到2006年，他曾擔任[[塔爾薩縣|塔爾薩縣]]及[[瓦戈納縣_(奧克拉荷馬州)|瓦戈納縣]]的[[俄克拉何马州参议院|州參議員]]；2001年時也曾於{{link-en|奧克拉荷馬州第一國會選區|Oklahoma's 1st congressional district|州第一選區}}[[美國眾議院|聯邦眾議員]]{{le|史蒂夫·拉金特|Steve Largent}}不再尋求連任時競逐眾議員席位，但最後在初選敗給[[約翰·蘇利文|約翰·蘇利文]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thegreenpapers.com/G02/OK.phtml |title=Oklahoma 2002 Midterm Election |accessdate=2016-12-08 |archive-date=2017-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170209174132/http://www.thegreenpapers.com/G02/OK.phtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。是一名著名的[[全球变暖|全球变暖]]怀疑者。<ref>BBC新闻网：Scott Pruitt: Controversial Trump environment nominee sworn in：http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-39010374 {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-39010374 |date=20170220100306 }}</ref>

2006年他不再參選州參議員，轉而{{le|2006年奧克拉荷馬州選舉|Oklahoma state elections, 2006|競逐}}{{le|奧克拉荷馬州副州長|Lieutenant Governor of Oklahoma}}，唯於初選中輸給{{le|托德·希特|Todd Hiett}}；至2010年，他當選為奧克拉荷馬州檢察長<ref name="officalresults">{{cite web |url=http://www.ok.gov/elections/documents/General%20Election%20Results%20by%20County%20110210.pdf |publisher=Oklahoma State Election Board |title=Election Results |accessdate=2010-11-09 |format=pdf |archive-date=2010-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101116083917/http://www.ok.gov/elections/documents/General%20Election%20Results%20by%20County%20110210.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年12月7日，{{le|候任美國總統|President-elect of the United States}}[[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]提名普魯特出任{{le|美國環境保護局局長|Administrator of the Environmental Protection Agency}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-trump-epa-idUSKBN13W2HE|title=Trump to tap Oklahoma attorney general to lead EPA: transition team|date=December 7, 2016|publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|accessdate=2016-12-08|archive-date=2016-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161208135709/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-trump-epa-idUSKBN13W2HE|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他于2018年7月5日递交辞呈<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cnn.com/2018/07/05/politics/scott-pruitt-epa-resigns/index.html|title=EPA chief Scott Pruitt resigns amid ethics scandals|last=CNN|first=Jeremy Diamond, Eli Watkins and Juana Summers,|work=CNN|access-date=July 5, 2018|archive-date=2018-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180705195635/https://www.cnn.com/2018/07/05/politics/scott-pruitt-epa-resigns/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2018/07/05/scott-pruitts-full-resignation-letter-to-president-trump.html|title=Scott Pruitt's full resignation letter to President Trump|date=July 5, 2018|work=Fox News|access-date=July 5, 2018|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180705203756/http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2018/07/05/scott-pruitts-full-resignation-letter-to-president-trump.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

